long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension will allow you do search with both Google and ChatGPT. Just type in your search questions and key words, the extension will automatically query ChatGPT and display the responses from ChatGPT. You can also copy the result to clipboard and paste to your favorite text editors. Try it out now and it is FREE!
